data.description: So much to be THANKFUL for in this adorable house!! This is a 3 bedroom 2 full bath with a FULL basement with a finished den/family room.  This front covered porch with a swing is perfect to enjoy this great FALL weather and coffee. This home features split bedrooms and brand new beautiful hardwood floors and carpet in the bedrooms.  The living room is spacious and open to the dining room. The kitchen has stainless fridge, stove and microwave. The dishwasher is black to match the cabinets. Downstairs has nice size finished den/family room with a storage closet with new lights. The garage has new awesome LED lights to brighten up the area. The back deck is covered with brand new steps and support post overlooking the great fenced in backyard.  Under the deck is a great patio area to enjoy everything outside.
